dssqlddl:
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW CRMVLEADS AS SELECT a.ETAPA as ETAPA,a.ORDEN as ORDEN,aa.PIPELINE as PIPELINE,ab.DESCRIPCION as DESCRIPCION,ab.ALTA as ALTA,ab.FECTSTART as FECTSTART,ab.IMPORTEPREV as IMPORTEPREV,ab.OPORTUNIDAD as OPORTUNIDAD,ab.POSITION as POSITION,ab.PROBABILIDAD as PROBABILIDAD,ab.IDCRMPIPELINE0 as IDCRMPIPELINE0,ab.IDCRMETAPA0 as IDCRMETAPA0,ab.IDXOPORTUNIDAD as IDXOPORTUNIDAD FROM CRMOPORTUNIDAD ab
 INNER JOIN 
CRMETAPA a ON a.IDXCRMETAPA = ab.IDCRMETAPA0 INNER JOIN 
CRMPIPELINE aa ON aa.IDXCRMPIPELINE = ab.IDCRMPIPELINE0 WHERE   ab.ARCHIVED= false;
